               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182201090051"></xptr>CONNER'S Defence. I was distressed - and when it was given to me, I was taking it home.</p>
               <p>SIMMONDS'S Defence. I saw them running away, and waited to see if they were taken.</p>
